
## Manipulating Directories

cd
cd -
cd ..
cd ../..

pwd

mkdir
rmdir
rmdir -f 
rm -r

ls
mv

find . -name "filename"
find directory -nale "filename"
(we can use regex to search for filenames)


## Manipulating Files

touch
touch directory/file
(we can use absolute or relative path)

vi
gedit

./file.py

grep
grep -r


## Manipulating Permissions

sudo
sudo su

chmod 


## Special

& (run in the background)
&& (run in parallel)
| (pipe)

> (std output redirection)
2> (error redirection)
>> (append stdout)
2>> (append err)


## Looping in bash
use bash loop
or by writing a python script importing os

